General Assembly Raised Bill No. 520
February Session, 2026 LCO No. 3609
Referred to Committee on GOVERNMENT OVERSIGHT
Introduced by:
(GOS)
AN ACT REPEALING A CONVEYANCE OF A PARCEL OF STATE
LAND TO THE TOWN OF CANTON.
Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives in General
Assembly convened:
1 Section 1. Special act 24-20 is repealed. (Effective from passage)
This act shall take effect as follows and shall amend the following
sections:
Section 1 from passage Repealer section
Statement of Purpose:
To repeal special act 24-20, which required the conveyance of a parcel of
state land to the town of Canton.
